This paper discusses the optimization of wireless access networks, which falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also discusses interference management and resource allocation, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions spatial reuse factor optimization, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and data compression (cs.DC).
